data.description: Defines a row in a Decision Matrix. The label for this object is Decision Matrix Row.

schema.description: [Tech] Defines a row in a Decision Matrix. The label for this object is Decision Matrix Row.

Id.title: Decision Matrix Row ID
Id.description: Globally unique string that identifies a record.

LastModifiedDate.title: Last Modified Date
LastModifiedDate.description: Date and time when a user last modified this record.

IsVersionEnabled.title: Version Enabled
IsVersionEnabled.description: Specifies whether the associated matrix version is active. Derived from the associated Decision Matrix Version (CalculationMatrixVersion object).

StartDateTime.title: Start Date Time
StartDateTime.description: The first date on which this row version is active. Applicable if IsVersionEnabled is true.

EndDateTime.title: End Date Time
EndDateTime.description: The last date on which this row version is active. Applicable if IsVersionEnabled is true.

InputData.title: Input Data
InputData.description: The input columns and associated values for this row of the matrix.

OutputData.title: Output Data
OutputData.description: The output columns and associated values for this row of the matrix.
